data.description: Custom built home in a quiet dead end street! This is a 3 Bedroom 2 Bath house that features: main floor living with kitchen and dining that has an open concept feel, laundry off of the kitchen and an additional 912 Sq Ft Family/Bonus room on the lower Level. Seller has updated the flooring throughout the main level. Oversized attached garage, newer front deck and plenty of parking and fenced back yard. Call Today for a showing!
